text: Söderhamns UIF is a sports club in the town of Söderhamn in Sweden. The club was established in 1960. The club won the Swedish national men's table tennis team championship in the years of 1978, 1982, 1985, 2001 and 2010. ==References== ==Other websites== *Official website Category:1960 establishments in Europe Category:Table tennis clubs in Sweden Category:1960s establishments in Sweden
